				<outline text="The Gates keynote was borrrring (no surprise) so I left early and came over to the Bloghaus blogging party. Here's a &lt;a href=&quot;http://blip.tv/file/127943&quot;&gt;movie&lt;/a&gt; of the scene." created="Mon, 08 Jan 2007 04:33:03 GMT" type="outline"/>
